<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥٧ و ٣٥٨)</span> وابن منده في <span class="c1">" التوحيد "</span> <span class="c2">(ق ٣٩ / ٢)</span> وابن عدي <span class="c2">(٢٦٣ / ٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
